@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>At TicketManager, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your personal data when you use our services.</p>

<h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Account details: Name, email address, login credentials</li>
    <li>Ticket and event activity: Purchases, preferences, reviews</li>
    <li>Device and usage data: IP address, browser type, cookies, referring URLs</li>
    <li>Payment information: Processed securely via Stripe and PayPal</li>
</ul>

<h3>2. Analytics & Tracking</h3>
<ul>
    <li>We use Google Analytics to understand site usage and improve user experience</li>
    <li>Third-party cookies may track user behavior for service enhancement and security</li>
    <li>You can disable cookies in your browser or opt out of tracking via third-party tools</li>
</ul>

<h3>3. Third-Party Services</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Payment providers (Stripe, PayPal) handle financial transactions securely</li>
    <li>Email services (e.g., SendGrid) may be used for notifications and communications</li>
    <li>Social media widgets may collect interaction data if used</li>
</ul>

<h3>4. How We Use Your Information</h3>
<ul>
    <li>To process transactions and send order confirmations</li>
    <li>To improve platform features and customer support</li>
    <li>To personalize content and recommend relevant events</li>
</ul>

<h3>5. Data Protection</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Data is encrypted in transit and at rest when possible</li>
    <li>Access is restricted to authorized staff and service providers</li>
    <li>We comply with GDPR and other applicable regulations for user privacy</li>
</ul>

<h3>6. Your Rights</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Access, correction, or deletion of personal data on request</li>
    <li>Right to object to data processing or restrict use</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent for marketing communications at any time</li>
</ul>

<h3>7. Changes to This Policy</h3>
<p>This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. We will notify you of significant changes via email or platform notices.</p>

<h3>8. Contact Us</h3>
<p>Questions or concerns? Reach out to <a href="mailto:support@ticketmanager.com">support@ticketmanager.com</a>.</p>
